===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A strip of [[leather]].
# {{italbrac|British|US}} An undergarment or swimwear consisting of very narrow strips designed to cover just the genitals and nothing more.
# {{cattag|Australian|US}} An item of footwear, usually of rubber, secured by two straps mounted between the big toe and its neighbour.

